general.name: ssppTargets
general.description: The SEGUE targeting information for all fibers associated with a given data release. The format is the same as the full target files . For the SEGUE-2 spectroscopic parameters associated with each star, see the associated ssppOut file. This file is simply gathered from the matches to each individual plate, the segueTargetPlate files.
